sentences: Choi Soo-young (Korean: 최수영; born February 10, 1990), professionally known as Sooyoung, is a South Korean singer, actress and songwriter.
She was a member of the short-lived Korean-Japanese singing duo Route 0 during 2002 in Japan.

After returning to South Korea in 2004, Sooyoung eventually became a member of girl group Girls' Generation in 2007, which went on to become one of the best-selling artists in South Korea and one of South Korea's most popular girl groups worldwide.
